                        wir <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> kein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> getan <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu ist uns niht wissend, daz uns kein
                        brief von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> von der
                        sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sey. Also <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        ewr gnade <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir uns gen
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>riczen</ex></expan> niht<pb facs="#facs_132" id="65r"/> vergahen,
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>darinn<ex>en</ex></expan> meynen zu gefarn, daz wir wol getrawen zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
